[{"question":"So it\u0027s quite a messy situation, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"That\u0027s right.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":75,"aSentId":76},{"question":"Could you explain what that means?","answer":"Yes, that\u0027s right.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":95,"aSentId":96},{"question":"Are you concerned about the kind of celebrification of her through this case and the kind of pressure that will now put on her when she tries to return to normal life?","answer":"THE TRIALS OF AMANDA KNOX\": Well, I don\u0027t know that there\u0027s been a lot of celebrification going on as much as demonization.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":114,"aSentId":115},{"question":"How have they all been bearing up?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s been incredibly difficult, Piers.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":126,"aSentId":127},{"question":"Do you believe that she was guilty of lying?","answer":"No, I don\u0027t.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":145,"aSentId":146},{"question":"Thomas, I mean, do you believe the family feel so angry about the defamation conviction that they may seek to have that overturned?","answer":"I can\u0027t speak for the family.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":165,"aSentId":166},{"question":"What was your overall take of the whole thing?","answer":"You know, Piers, my overall take was there was nothing that I could glean from this young lady\u0027s history that suggested anything like the way she was portrayed in the Italian press or by the -- by the prosecutors in this case.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":189,"aSentId":190},{"question":"But from your assessment what kind of woman is Amanda Knox?","answer":"There\u0027s two things I want to comment on that, Piers.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":203,"aSentId":204},{"question":"What is your primary motivation in going public now?","answer":"Well, Piers, Michael is no longer with us, obviously.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":225,"aSentId":226},{"question":"Did you find that with him?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":249,"aSentId":250},{"question":"Like a good businessman, would you say?","answer":"Yes, Michael had great instincts, particularly with regard to marketing and promotion.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":254,"aSentId":255},{"question":"He must have thought you were a genius, didn\u0027t he?","answer":"Well, Michael was the genius.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":264,"aSentId":265},{"question":"But in terms of the Beatles music, is that still part of Michael\u0027s estate?","answer":"Absolutely, yes.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":287,"aSentId":288},{"question":"And in terms of the sheer number crunching here, could you tell me now what he paid for it and what it might now be worth?","answer":"Well, we bought the catalog in 1985.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":289,"aSentId":290},{"question":"So he took it from 40-odd million to $1 billion?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":296,"aSentId":297},{"question":"What kind of decisions have you taken which have turned out to be very smart ones in relation to handling his estate?","answer":"Well, my co-executor John MaClean and I -- let\u0027s face it, Piers, we\u0027re fortunate to represent Michael Jackson.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":305,"aSentId":306},{"question":"What would you say to that?","answer":"I\u0027m not sure if that\u0027s true or not.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":316,"aSentId":317},{"question":"How did he seem to you?","answer":"It wasn\u0027t a long meeting.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":340,"aSentId":341},{"question":"In all your experience of working in the entertainment industry, how did Michael\u0027s business empire rank?","answer":"Michael truly was one of a kind.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":356,"aSentId":357},{"question":"But was his spending out of control, as people kept saying it was?","answer":"Well, that was an area that was handled by Michael\u0027s business managers and accountants.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":375,"aSentId":376},{"question":"How do their estates compare in terms of how you manage them?","answer":"Well, it\u0027s hard to compare.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":384,"aSentId":385},{"question":"How fast have those assets appreciated since his death?","answer":"Well, you know, we\u0027ve tried to do the right things.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":393,"aSentId":394},{"question":"Am I right in thinking the estate is already petitioned to distribute 30 million dollars to the will\u0027s beneficiaries, who would be his immediate family and children?","answer":"Yeah.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":412,"aSentId":413},{"question":"John, presumably as the co-executor, would you have read the will to the family?","answer":"Yes, I did, to Mrs. Jackson and several of Michael\u0027s siblings.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":420,"aSentId":421},{"question":"How was that?","answer":"Very emotional.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":423,"aSentId":424},{"question":"Were you aware that that 2002 will was still in play?","answer":"No, not at all.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":433,"aSentId":434},{"question":"Are they in a more relaxed frame of mind about it?","answer":"I would think so.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":440,"aSentId":441},{"question":"Is that right?","answer":"That\u0027s true, Piers.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":451,"aSentId":452},{"question":"Is that right?","answer":"That\u0027s right.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":484,"aSentId":485},{"question":"In 2013, it goes to Vegas permanently and there will be a Michael Jackson Museum?","answer":"There will be another show that\u0027s created permanently and specifically for a theater in Las Vegas in 2013.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":497,"aSentId":498},{"question":"What do you make of all this?","answer":"The issue in this case will be, did Conrad Murray engage in the appropriate standard of care for a physician in that situation.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":502,"aSentId":503},{"question":"What do you think of that?","answer":"I think the pressures of any allegations, even though they\u0027re false and even though it turns out you\u0027re acquitted, put tremendous pressure on you.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":516,"aSentId":517},{"question":"What did you think of his status as a performer?","answer":"I think it was unparalleled.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":526,"aSentId":527},{"question":"What do you think his legacy will be?","answer":"As Berry Gordy said, the greatest performer who ever lived.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":531,"aSentId":532},{"question":"Howard?","answer":"For me, when people ask me to describe Michael Jackson, I say push the play button on the video or on your iPod and that says it all.","docId":"111003pmt","qSentId":533,"aSentId":534}]